<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Consumer - Account Setup</title>
    <link href="css/theme.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/consumer_account_setup.css">
    <style>
        /* Basic reset for preview consistency */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Site Header -->
    <header class="modern-header" id="consumerHeader">
    </header>
    <div class="consumer-account-setup consumer-getting-started">
        <!-- Sidebar Overlay -->
        <div id="sidebar-overlay" class="sidebar-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <!-- Mobile Menu Toggle -->
        <button id="mobile-menu-toggle" class="mobile-menu-toggle" aria-label="Toggle navigation menu"
            aria-expanded="false">
            <i class="fa fa-bars"></i>
        </button>
        <!-- Sidebar -->
       <div id="consumerSidebar">

       </div>
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="cas-main" id="main-content">
            <div class="cas-content-wrapper">
                <!-- Breadcrumb -->
                <nav id="cas_breadcrumb" class="cas-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
                    <a onclick="load_page('index')">Docs</a>
                    <span class="separator"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
                    <a onclick="load_page('consumer_docs_home')">Consumer</a>
                    <span class="separator"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
                    <span class="current">Account Setup</span>
                </nav>
                <!-- Page Title -->
                <h1 id="cas_title" class="cas-page-title">Account Setup & Verification</h1>
                <p class="cas-page-subtitle">Learn how to register your mPay Consumer Wallet account, complete identity
                    verification and configure your profile preferences.</p>
                <!-- Registration Section -->
                <section id="cas_content_registration" class="doc-section">
                    <h2 id="registration">Registration</h2>
                    <p>
                        Creating your mPay Consumer Wallet account is quick and straightforward. All you need is a valid
                        phone number to get started. </p>
                    <h3 id="phone-registration">Wallet Registration</h3>
                    <p>
                        Your mobile number and e-mail address serve as one of the unique identifier in the mPay Network.
                        Follow these steps to register or sign up: </p>
                    <div class="steps-container">
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">1</div>
                            <h4>Are you an existing mPay Customer?</h4>
                            <p> On the welcome screen, you will be prompted to select whether you <strong>"Are an
                                    existing customer?"</strong>. For new customers, tap the <strong>NO</strong> button.
                                If you already have an account, select <strong>YES</strong> button instead.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">2</div>
                            <h4>Enroll New Customer Form</h4>
                            <p>User is taken to <strong> Enroll New Consumer </strong> form.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">3</div>
                            <h4>Required Customer Information</h4>
                            <p>The <strong> User ID </strong>, <strong> E-mail Address </strong>, and <strong>Mobile
                                    Number</strong> should be unique for each customers. </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">4</div>
                            <h4>Create Your PIN</h4>
                            <p>Set a 6-digit PIN that you'll use to authorize transactions and access your wallet.
                                Choose something secure but memorable.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">5</div>
                            <h4>Accept Terms of Service</h4>
                            <p>Review and accept the mPay Network <a onclick="load_page('terms_of_service')"
                                    style="color: var(--color-primary); cursor: pointer;">Terms of Service</a> and <a
                                    onclick="load_page('privacy_policy')"
                                    style="color: var(--color-primary); cursor: pointer;">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">6</div>
                            <h4>Security Questions setup</h4>
                            <p>Setup security question, which will be used for account recovery and password reset.
                                Click on <strong>Submit</strong> button</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">7</div>
                            <h4>OTP Verification</h4>
                            <p>An SMS will be sent to your registered mobile number with <strong>OTP(One-Time PIN).
                                </strong></p>
                            <p>Ensure to verify the correct OTP. </p>
                            <p> Success message will be displayed that Registration is successful, tap
                                <strong>OK</strong> button. </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">8</div>
                            <h4>PIN Configuration</h4>
                            <p> Customer is <strong>required</strong> to setup a PIN for the wallet application. </p>
                            <p><strong title="Personal Identification Number">PIN</strong> acts as your application's
                                secure passcode.</p>
                            <p>Users are required to enter their PIN each time they log in to verify their identity and
                                access the application.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">9</div>
                            <h4>Biometrics Setup for Login</h4>
                            <p> Customer can also use biometrics data to sign in to the wallet application as an added
                                layer of security.</p>
                            <p>If biometrics is setup, we use <strong>Face ID</strong> or <strong>Touch ID</strong> to
                                sign in to the wallet application <strong>by default.</strong></p>
                        </div>
                </section>
                <div class="callout callout-info">
                    <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>
                    <div class="callout-content">
                        <strong>Security Tip</strong>
                        It is recommended to keep both security measures enabled to ensure stronger protection for your
                        wallet application.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Supported Regions -->
                <br>
                <br />
                <h3 id="supported-regions">Supported Regions</h3>
                <p>
                    mPay Consumer Wallet is currently available in the following regions: </p>
                <ul style="list-style-type: square;  margin-left: 40px">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Curaçao</strong>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <!-- HIDE FOR NOW AS PER AMAR
		  <li>United Kingdom (+44)</li>
          <li>European Union (multiple country codes)</li> 
          <li>Canada (+1)</li>
          <li>Australia (+61)</li>
          <li>Select Asian and African markets — see the app for the full list</li>  -->
                <div class="callout callout-warning">
                    <i class="fa fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                    <div class="callout-content">
                        <strong>VoIP numbers not supported</strong>
                        Virtual phone numbers (Google Voice, Skype, etc.) are not accepted for registration. You must
                        use a mobile carrier number.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Identity Verification Section -->
                <section id="cas_content_verification" class="doc-section">
                    <h2 id="identity-verification">Identity Verification</h2>
                    <p>
                        mPay needs to verify its customer's identity to prevent fraud. Please refer below to learn more
                        about customer's profile status: </p>
                    <h3 id="verification-tiers">Wallet Account Status</h3>
                    <div class="tier-cards">
                        <div class="tier-card">
                            <span class="tier-badge basic">Incomplete Profile</span>
                            <h4>Newly Enrolled User</h4>
                            <div class="tier-limit"> <span> </span>
                            </div>
                            <ul class="tier-features">
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Account created
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Need to complete profile
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> To Upload ID documents
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Limited Access
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tier-card recommended">
                            <span class="tier-badge standard">Not Verified</span>
                            <h4>Waiting for Verification</h4>
                            <div class="tier-limit"> <span></span>
                            </div>
                            <ul class="tier-features">
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Has Completed Profile
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Uploaded ID Documents
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Profile is<strong>Pending</strong>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Limited Access
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Verification process up to 48 hours
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tier-card">
                            <span class="tier-badge premium">Verified</span>
                            <h4>Profile Fully Verified</h4>
                            <div class="tier-limit"> <span></span>
                            </div>
                            <ul class="tier-features">
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Identity was verified
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Full access
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Manage Wallet Account
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Send/Receive Funds
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Advanced analytics
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 id="verification-process">How to Verify Your Identity</h3>
                    <p>
                        After a successful registration, login to your mPay Wallet application to <strong>Complete the
                            Profile </strong> by uploading pertinent identification documents. </p>
                    <div class="steps-container">
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">1</div>
                            <h4>Enter address details and other required information</h4>
                            <p>Make sure the address matched with the government-issued ID to be submitted in the
                                verification process.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">2</div>
                            <h4>Upload Government-Issued ID</h4>
                            <p>Take a clear photo of your valid government-issued identification. Supported documents
                                include passports, national ID cards, and driver's licenses.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">3</div>
                            <h4>Take a photo for your profile picture</h4>
                            <p>Take a live selfie for facial comparison. Our system matches your face against your ID
                                photo. Ensure good lighting and remove accessories like sunglasses.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">4</div>
                            <h4>Wait for Review</h4>
                            <p>mPay Network will carefully review all customer&apos;s details and may take 24 to 48
                                hours for verification process to complete. Whatever the result of the verification
                                process, customer will be verified via SMS and email.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 id="required-documents">Required Documents</h3>
                    <div class="doc-table-wrapper">
                        <table class="doc-table">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Document</th>
                                    <th>Consumer</th>
                                    <th>Merchant</th>
                                    <th>Notes</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Government ID (Passport / National ID / Driver's License)</td>
                                    <td><span class="status-badge required"><i class="fa fa-asterisk"></i>
                                            Required</span></td>
                                    <td><span class="status-badge required"><i class="fa fa-asterisk"></i>
                                            Required</span></td>
                                    <td>Must be valid and unexpired</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Selfie Photo</td>
                                    <td><span class="status-badge required"><i class="fa fa-asterisk"></i>
                                            Required</span></td>
                                    <td><span class="status-badge required"><i class="fa fa-asterisk"></i>
                                            Required</span></td>
                                    <td>Live capture, no uploads</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Proof of Address</td>
                                    <td><span class="status-badge optional"><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Optional</span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td><span class="status-badge required"><i class="fa fa-asterisk"></i>
                                            Required</span></td>
                                    <td>Utility bill, bank statement (last 3 months)</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Tax Identification Number</td>
                                    <td><span class="status-badge optional"><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Optional</span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td><span class="status-badge required"><i class="fa fa-asterisk"></i>
                                            Required</span></td>
                                    <td>SSN, TIN, or equivalent</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <div class="callout callout-success">
                        <i class="fa fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        <div class="callout-content">
                            <strong>Your data is secure</strong>
                            All documents are encrypted end-to-end and processed by our certified KYC partner. We never
                            store raw images after verification is complete. See our <a
                                onclick="load_page('privacy_policy')"
                                style="color: #166534; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline;">Privacy Policy</a>
                            for details.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 id="verification-status">Checking Verification Status</h3>
                    <p>
                        You can check your current verification status at any time: </p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Open the mPay app and login.</li>
                        <li>Depending on the customer&apos;s status, user will receive message after login:</li>
                    </ol>
                    <p><b>
                            Status indicators: </b></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong style="color: #22c55e;"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Verified</strong> — You
                            can access the app functionalities. During the first time login after account has been
                            verified, you will get a message <strong>"Congratulations! Your account has been fully
                                verified!"</strong>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong style="color: #f59e0b;"><i class="fa fa-clock"></i> Pending</strong> — Under review
                            and will display a message that <strong>"Your account is still under review." </strong>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong style="color: #ef4444;"><i class="fa fa-times-circle"></i> Rejected</strong> —
                            customer will see a message <strong>There's a problem with your account, please contact
                                support@mpaynetwork.com for more details.</strong>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                <!-- Profile Configuration Section -->
                <section id="cas_content_profile" class="doc-section">
                    <h2 id="profile-configuration">Profile Configuration</h2>
                    <p>
                        Customize your mPay profile so that friends and merchants can easily identify you during
                        transactions. </p>
                    <div class="profile-preview">
                        <div class="profile-avatar-placeholder">
                            <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="profile-details">
                            <p class="profile-name">Alex Johnson</p>
                            <p class="profile-phone">+1 (555) 012-3456</p>
                            <p class="profile-status"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Account Verified</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 id="profile-fields">Profile Fields</h3>
                    <div class="config-grid">
                        <div class="config-item">
                            <div class="config-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="config-text">
                                <h5>Full Name</h5>
                                <p>The name shown to others during transactions. Can be your real name or a nickname.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="config-item">
                            <div class="config-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-camera"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="config-text">
                                <h5>Profile Photo</h5>
                                <p>Upload a photo or take a new one. Optional but recommended for P2P transfers.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="config-item">
                            <div class="config-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="config-text">
                                <h5>Email Address</h5>
                                <p>Used for transaction receipts and account recovery. Strongly recommended.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="config-item">
                            <div class="config-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-globe"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="config-text">
                                <h5>Preferred Language</h5>
                                <p>Set your display language. Currently supports English, Spanish, French, German, and
                                    Portuguese.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="config-item">
                            <div class="config-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-dollar-sign"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="config-text">
                                <h5>QR Profile</h5>
                                <p>Your profile QR to use in receiving money to your wallet account.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="config-item">
                            <div class="config-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-bell"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="config-text">
                                <h5>Notification Preferences</h5>
                                <p>Configure push notifications, email alerts, and SMS for payment and security events.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 id="edit-profile">Editing Your Profile</h3>
                    <p>To <b>edit</b> your profile information:</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>1. Open the mPay app</li>
                        <li>2. Tap the <strong>profile icon</strong> in the top-right corner (or navigate to
                            <strong>Settings &rarr; Profile</strong>)
                        </li>
                        <li>3. Tap the <strong>&quot;Edit&quot;</strong> button next to the field you want to change
                        </li>
                        <li>4. Make your changes and tap <strong>&quot;Save&quot;</strong>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="code-block">
                    </div>
                    <div class="callout callout-info">
                        <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>
                        <div class="callout-content">
                            <strong>Changing your phone number is subject for mPay Network&apos;s approval and
                                verification</strong>
                            Call the mPay hotline or send an e-mail to support@mpaynetwork.com.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 id="security-setup">Initial Security Setup</h3>
                    <p>
                        During account setup, we strongly recommend configuring these security features: </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Biometric Authentication:</strong> Enable fingerprint or Face ID for quick, secure
                            access
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Transaction PIN:</strong> Your 6-digit PIN is required for all transactions — never
                            share it with anyone
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="callout callout-danger">
                        <i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
                        <div class="callout-content">
                            <strong>Never share your PIN or OTP codes</strong>
                            mPay will never ask for your PIN or OTP via phone, email, or chat. Anyone requesting these
                            is attempting fraud. Report suspicious activity immediately through the app.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <!-- FAQ Section -->
                <section id="cas_faq_accordion" class="doc-section faq-section">
                    <h2 id="faq">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-1">
                            <span>Can I register with a phone number from a different country?</span>
                            <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-1" role="region">
                            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                Yes, you can register with any supported country code. However, some features may be
                                limited based on your registration region. Transaction limits and available features may
                                vary by country due to local regulations.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-2">
                            <span>How long does identity verification take?</span>
                            <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-2" role="region">
                            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                Tier 2 (Standard) verification is automated and typically completes within 5 minutes.
                                Tier 3 (Premium) verification may require manual review and can take up to 48 business
                                hours. You'll receive a push notification when the review is complete.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-3">
                            <span>What happens if my verification is rejected?</span>
                            <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-3" role="region">
                            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                If your verification is rejected, you'll receive a notification with the specific reason
                                (e.g., blurry photo, expired document, name mismatch). You can re-submit your documents
                                from <strong>Settings → Account → Verification</strong>. There is no limit to
                                re-submission attempts, but repeated failures may trigger a temporary cooldown period.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-4">
                            <span>Can I change my display name after registration?</span>
                            <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-4" role="region">
                            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                Yes, you can change your display name at any time from <strong>Settings → Profile → Edit
                                    Profile</strong>. Note that if you've completed Tier 2 or Tier 3 verification, your
                                legal name on file cannot be changed without re-verification. Your display name (shown
                                to other users) is separate from your legal name.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-5">
                            <span>I didn't receive the OTP code. What should I do?</span>
                            <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-5" role="region">
                            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                Wait at least 60 seconds, then tap "Resend Code". If you still don't receive it: (1)
                                ensure your phone has signal, (2) check that your number is correct, (3) check your
                                spam/blocked messages folder, (4) try restarting your phone. If the issue persists,
                                visit our <a onclick="load_page('consumer_troubleshooting')"
                                    style="color: var(--color-primary); cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline;">Troubleshooting
                                    page</a>.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-6">
                            <span>Is my personal data safe during verification?</span>
                            <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-6" role="region">
                            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                                Absolutely. All documents are transmitted using end-to-end encryption (AES-256). Our KYC
                                verification is handled by a certified, SOC 2 Type II compliant partner. Raw document
                                images are deleted after verification is complete. Only the verification result and a
                                hash are stored. Read more in our <a onclick="load_page('privacy_policy')"
                                    style="color: var(--color-primary); cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline;">Privacy
                                    Policy</a>.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <!-- Prev / Next Navigation -->
                <nav id="cas_prev_next" class="prev-next-nav" aria-label="Page navigation">
                    <div class="prev-next-card" onclick="load_page('consumer_getting_started')" role="link" tabindex="0"
                        aria-label="Previous page: Getting Started">
                        <span class="prev-next-label"><i class="fa fa-arrow-left"></i> Previous</span>
                        <span class="prev-next-title">Getting Started</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="prev-next-card next" onclick="load_page('consumer_making_payments')" role="link"
                        tabindex="0" aria-label="Next page: Making Payments">
                        <span class="prev-next-label">Next <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
                        <span class="prev-next-title">Making Payments</span>
                    </div>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </main>
        <!-- Table of Contents (visible on wide screens) -->
        <aside class="cas-toc" role="navigation" aria-label="Table of contents">
            <div class="cas-toc-title">On this page</div>
            <ul class="cas-toc-list">
                <li>
                    <a href="#registration">Registration</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#phone-registration">Phone Number Registration</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#supported-regions">Supported Regions</a>
